  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Judofuri is a local party game for <strong>up to 9 players</strong>, where you face off in a variety of easy-to-pickup, fast-paced <strong>mini-games.</strong> Bring your friends and family and embrace the chaos! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONE BUTTON ONLY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each player needs one, and <strong>ONLY one</strong> button to compete in Judofuri. <strong>ONE BUTTON!</strong> No joystick, no mouse movement, just <strong>ONE. SINGLE. BUTTON.</strong> And you get to choose yours at the beginning of each session! A mouse click, a gamepad trigger, a spacebar, <strong>anything works.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>20 MINI-GAMES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through hurdles, chop vegetables, train your cardio, fish, and more! Each mini-game is <strong>unique</strong> and requires a <strong>different</strong> skill, so everyone gets their opportunity to shine.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY ONLINE WITH YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Judofuri is fully compatible with <strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong>. Only one of you needs to <strong>own the game</strong>, the rest of your online squad can just join through Steam <strong>in a few clicks!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SHARE THE CONTROLLER, IF NEEDED</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't have enough gamepads for your couch gaming session? If you've been following so far, you should remember you only need <strong>ONE</strong> button to play : You can <strong>share</strong> the <strong>same gamepad</strong> (or keyboard) between 2, 3, even 9 players! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Judofuri is a local party game for <strong>up to 9 players</strong>, where you face off in a variety of easy-to-pickup, fast-paced <strong>mini-games.</strong> Bring your friends and family and embrace the chaos! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONE BUTTON ONLY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each player needs one, and <strong>ONLY one</strong> button to compete in Judofuri. <strong>ONE BUTTON!</strong> No joystick, no mouse movement, just <strong>ONE. SINGLE. BUTTON.</strong> And you get to choose yours at the beginning of each session! A mouse click, a gamepad trigger, a spacebar, <strong>anything works.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>20 MINI-GAMES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through hurdles, chop vegetables, train your cardio, fish, and more! Each mini-game is <strong>unique</strong> and requires a <strong>different</strong> skill, so everyone gets their opportunity to shine.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY ONLINE WITH YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Judofuri is fully compatible with <strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong>. Only one of you needs to <strong>own the game</strong>, the rest of your online squad can just join through Steam <strong>in a few clicks!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SHARE THE CONTROLLER, IF NEEDED</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't have enough gamepads for your couch gaming session? If you've been following so far, you should remember you only need <strong>ONE</strong> button to play : You can <strong>share</strong> the <strong>same gamepad</strong> (or keyboard) between 2, 3, even 9 players! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.poster.avif?t=1774457671\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.webm?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.mp4?t=1774457671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
